  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL18">
<l>iṉitirait tivalai mōta eṟiyuntaṇ paravai mītē</l>
<l>taṉikiṭan taracu ceyyun tāmaraik kaṇṇa ṉemmāṉ</l>
<l>kaṉiyirun taṉaiya cevvāyk kaṇṇaṇaik kaṇṭa kaṇkaḷ</l>
<l>paṉiyarum putiru mālō veṉceykēṉ pāvi yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Buds of tears drop down [from my] eyes</l>
<l>that have seen Kṛṣṇa with lips red like ripe fruit,</l>
<l>our Lord, the lotus-eyed [Lord] who rules [by] reclining on His own</l>
<l>upon the cool ocean that tosses [to and fro] as the spraying waves crash sweetly.</l>
<l rend="indent">Ālō! What shall I, a sinner, do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
